      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. and it's not just the altitude stuff. if you look at the way the telemetry was broadcast, there are huge gaps in the signal during the most critical moments of descent. it feels intentional, like they needed to cut the feed while they were approaching the site. if there was an actual structure there, like something built, that would explain why they had to create the \"hoax\" narrative to explain away the weirdness people might have seen. do you think the data gaps correlate with any specific sightings or reported \"objects\" in those redacted files?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
